snippet.title: Hoomeez First gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Hoomeez is a Multiplayer Casual Arcade game that grants the player control of a Hoomie, a cartoonish avatar that the player will use in competitive play across many small levels and matches with dozens of other players participating in it.

Play it on Gameup: https://gameup.ir/game/hoomeez
Twitter: https://twitter.com/hoomeez_game
Telegram:https://t.me/Hoomeez
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hoomeez_game/
Discord: https://discord.gg/vP9sjmDz9J
website:https://hoomeez.com/
